@startuml folio-activity-submit-peer-review
' Folio — Reviewer submits review (UC-04)
' Render: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml

title Submit peer review — activity (UC-04)

|Reviewer|
start
:Open accepted assignment;
:Read manuscript files;
:Enter author comments,\neditor-only notes, recommendation;
:Choose **Submit review**;

|System|
if (Assignment accepted and\ncomments valid?) then (yes)
  :Save review;
  :Set assignment = **completed**;
  :Notify editors / journal managers;
  |Reviewer|
  :Show confirmation;
  stop
else (no)
  |Reviewer|
  :Show validation error;
  stop
endif

@enduml
